    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is always so busy and it takes weeks just to get an appointment. i feel like i know my body better than anyone else. if i just take a break from the sertraline for a few days first to let it clear out of my system, wouldn't that make it safe to start the st john's wort? i just want something more natural that doesnt make me feel sick all the time.",
